-27-86" class="item-link" data-hovercard='p$t$cao-ya-27-86'><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-885147b74582919c83d02c96dd433ac1_l.jpg" alt="草芽君" class="avatar d50"></a></li></ul></div></div><div class="module"><div class="module-header"><h3><a href="/roundtable">查看全部圆桌活动 »</a></h3></div></div><div class="module"><div class="global-footer"><ul><li><a href="https://liukanshan.zhihu.com" target="_blank">刘看山</a></li><li><a href="javascript:;" id="js-feedback-button">建议反馈</a></li><li><a href="/app" target="_blank">移动应用</a></li><li><a href="/careers">招聘</a></li><li><a href="/question/19581624" target="_blank">知乎指南</a></li><li><a href="/terms" target="_blank">知乎协议</a></li><li><span class="copy">&copy; 2018 知乎 </span></li></ul></div></div></div></aside></main><script type="text/json" class="json-inline" data-name="guiders2">{}</script>
